三、教學目標 Objectives


教學目標：（一）認識我國優秀文化和科學精神，振興國人不斷探索和創造的精神。（二）正確地瞭解我國傳統文化與其他外來文化的交流與融合。（三）探討中國文化的歷史發展軌跡，並且瞭解現今狀況及其在世界歷史上的地      位與影響。 


Teaching Objectives:(A)to recognize China's outstanding cultural and scientific spirit, the revitalization of people continue to explore and create the spirit.(B)a correct understanding of our traditional culture and other foreign cultural exchanges and integration.(C)to explore the historical development of Chinese culture track, and understand the current situation and its history in the world bits and effects. 


